<p>Here, we know we have a <code>genusForm</code> variable. So... how can we render it? You can't
render! I'm kidding - you totally can, by using several special Twig functions that
Symfony gives us.</p>
<h2 id="the-form-twig-functions">The Form Twig Functions <a class="headerlink" href="render-form-bootstrap#the-form-twig-functions" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
