	                        <div id="dsq-comment-message-2773859035" class="dsq-comment-message">
	                            <div id="dsq-comment-text-2773859035" class="dsq-comment-text">
	                                <p>I don't understand the purpose of using <code>form_widget</code> inside twig, why do we need to use it?</p><p><code>{{ form_start(login_form) }}</code> this will generate all the form with its fields, labels etc...</p><p>The following code works fine with or without <code>form_widget</code>:</p><p></p><pre><code><br>{{ form_start(login_form) }}<br>{#{{ form_widget(login_form) }}#} <br>{{ form_end(login_form) }}<br></code></pre><p></p><p>Note: As I see <code>form_widget</code> will only append a <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> tag to the current form:<br></p><pre><code><br>&lt;div id="login_form"&gt;<br></code><br></pre><p></p><p>Am I wrong or ?</p>
	                            </div>
	                        </div>
	                    </div>
	                </li>
	            	        </ul>
	    </div>
            </div>

